text: KF Shemshova 1984 (, FK Šemševo 1984) is a football club based in the village of Shemshevë, Tetovo, North Macedonia. They are currently competing in the OFS Tetovo league. ==History== The club was founded in 1984. ==References== ==External links== *Shemshova 1984 Facebook *Club info at MacedonianFootball *Football Federation of Macedonia Shemshova 1984 Category:Association football clubs established in 1984 Category:1984 establishments in the Socialist Republic of Macedonia FK Shemshova
